		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Would it be possible to clip the original ROM pins in the middle and then solder the EPROM onto the old pins?
<br />
<br />It seems that you would be using the old pin solder sterngth and the new EPROM chip would just slide to either side for easy installing. And it's not like you're going to be using the old chip again anyways.

		

